-- Putin Seeks End of Offshore Companies in Strategic Sectors: RIA
-- B y   B r a d   C o o k
-- 2011-12-19T08:33:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-19/putin-seeks-end-of-offshore-companies-in-strategic-sectors-ria.html
Russian President  Vladimir Putin 
called for an end to the practice of Russian companies with
assets in strategic sectors of the economy registering companies
offshore, RIA Novosti reported today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
